 Purpose:
Container management and log viewing

Access Information:
- URL: portainer.lab.local
- Location (VM): apps.lab.local
- Container/Service Name: portainer (Docker Container)

Credentials:
- Admin Username: admin
- Admin Password Location: [in password manager]

Technical Details:
- Database: /opt/docker/portainer/portainer.db
- Configuration Files: /opt/docker/portainer/docker_config
- Data Location: /opt/docker/portainer
- Log Location: /var/lib/docker/containers/<container_id>/<container_id>-json.log

Common Operations:

Restart:
docker restart portainer

View Logs:
docker log | grep portainer

Check Status:
docker ps | grep portainer

Backup:
n/a

Dependencies:
- Requires: FreeIPA (DNS/IAM)
- Required by: n/a

Notes:
- Useful for docker management without CLI 
